== 調查 ==
伊朗當局事後立即下令調查這起空難<ref>{{cite web |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/video/middleeast/2011/01/2011110152020984432.html |title=Iran orders air-crash inquiry - Middle East |publisher=Al Jazeera English |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2011-01-11 |archive-date=2011-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110131163808/http://english.aljazeera.net/video/middleeast/2011/01/2011110152020984432.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。就在事故發生一天後，搜救隊尋獲了班機的[[飛行紀錄儀|飛行紀錄儀]]<ref name=FG351690>{{cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/2011/01/10/351690/both-recorders-retrieved-from-iran-air-727-crash-site.html |title=Both recorders retrieved from Iran Air 727 crash site |first=David |last=Kaminiski-Morrow |publisher=Flight International |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2011-01-11 |archive-date=2011-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110112173926/http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/2011/01/10/351690/both-recorders-retrieved-from-iran-air-727-crash-site.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[伊朗交通運輸部|伊朗交通運輸部]]亦表示，會組成若干個工作小組進行空難事件的調查，而[[伊朗民航組織|伊朗民航組織]]將負責監督調查作業<ref name=FG351648>{{cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/2011/01/10/351648/inquiry-opens-into-fatal-iran-air-727-crash.html |title=Inquiry opens into fatal Iran Air 727 crash |publisher=Flight International |date=2011-01-10 |accessdate=2011-01-11 |archive-date=2011-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110114191948/http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/2011/01/10/351648/inquiry-opens-into-fatal-iran-air-727-crash.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

